{"tid":1374892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佔領輿論；主動出擊】有冇辦法可以成立到連登新聞台？","createTime":"2019-07-28T02:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:54.000Z","uid":14480,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"00cff9ba6abb57a988ded53b68ab4a1a3fb48ebf","tid":1374892,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"用意 : <br />\n將每日新聞、記者會及重要資訊整合，製作懶人包(文字兼短片)，放於Youtube及Facebook，方便香港人用最短既時候，吸收最多既資訊，同時可以吸納到一班受眾，可以主導到輿論風向。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足點睇呢個idea，暫時小弟有時間可以每日都追新聞同記招，<br />\n但係整短片同整合資訊方面都需要人幫手，唔知各位手足點睇呢個idea?"},{"pid":"a2069a11ec2dbeb7de41d1d3ee346012023840d3","tid":1374892,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:30:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"3f7f00dddded26e48793adc5710ca0a7893557cd","tid":1374892,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:30:50.000Z","msg":"［需共識］齊上齊落 vs 自主撤水（集中討論）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374867</a>"},{"pid":"dd69a4a1e32ba45df23432aced1d2d40bfc6a7c2","tid":1374892,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcfb195c290cda0e5d2c0fbce07d76f1ee2cf7fa","tid":1374892,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"343ae13360bc97677020dd0f54718abe71315d13","tid":1374892,"uid":234658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f088e1f505d03d9b6769d2fb8959ba0f2789d13","tid":1374892,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:54.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！"}]}